<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link1047899" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=1047899&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F1439911-i-am-curious-i-watched-a-documentary%2Fanswers%2F1047899-sometimes-you-have-to">flag</a>
</div>
